                    text: "The 14 K4D is generally robust when maintained properly. Its main vulnerability is early supercharger coupler wear, not mechanical failure. Using correct 5W-20 oil, 95 RON fuel, and avoiding excessive heat/load greatly improves longevity. Post-mid-2016 models feature the updated coupler and show excellent reliability.",
