                    text: "The most frequent issues are supercharger coupler wear (pre-2016), high-pressure fuel pump failure due to poor oil or fuel, coolant leaks from plastic thermostat housing, and rear main seal oil leaks. These are documented in Land Rover service bulletins LTB00315 and TIS updates.",
