                    text: "The C 27 A1 offers smooth inline-six performance with mild-hybrid efficiency, but early models (2023–mid-2024) have BISG motor concerns. Mid-2024+ revisions improved durability significantly. With proper maintenance—especially oil changes using correct 5W-30 spec and avoiding excessive short trips—these engines can exceed 150,000 km reliably.",
