                    text: "The D 16 A8 offers smooth V6 diesel performance but early models (2016–2018) had timing chain tensioner issues. Post‑mid‑2018 revisions improved durability. With regular oil changes using ACEA C3 5W‑30, proper DPF regeneration through highway driving, and attention to fuel quality, it can be dependable beyond 200,000 km.",
