                    "@type": "Answer",
                    text: "The D16B2 offers strong low-end torque and refined diesel efficiency, but early models (2016–2017) had camshaft lobe concerns. Mid-2018 revisions improved durability. With proper maintenance—especially oil changes using 0W-30 STJLR.03.5034 and correct diesel fuel—well-cared-for examples can exceed 200,000 km reliably.",
