                    text: "Limited tuning potential due to OHV architecture and conservative ECU. Stage 1 remaps typically yield +10–15 kW safely. Bolt-on upgrades (exhaust, cold air intake) offer modest gains. Significant power increases require camshaft or displacement changes, which are uncommon due to complexity.",
